data.meta_description: Eyewear Express is locally owned and operated in Rhinelander, WI. Call (715)-365-1515 to schedule your optical eye exam.
data.text:
You keep telling yourself that your vision is just fine. Everyone squints when trying to read small print or make out a street sign in the dark, right? Wrong! When life starts getting a little blurry, you should check out the extensive services offered by Eyewear Express.

From thorough eye exams provided by licensed optometrists to designer glasses in every shape and color, you can count on us to take excellent care of your family's vision.

When finding a dedicated team of experienced professionals who truly cares about your eyes' health, Eyewear Express is the perfect place to start. We've been offering outstanding vision services in Rhinelander for over 30 years! Over that time, we've built an excellent reputation for efficient, caring, and quality services that will exceed your expectations every time!
